  "instructions": [
    "Toast cashews, walnuts, and macadamia nuts in a dry pan until fragrant.",
    "In a medium pot or saucepan, heat coconut oil over low heat.",
    "Add almond milk and cacao powder, stirring continuously to prevent burning. Allow it to simmer for about 5 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and fold in the soaked dates, toasted nuts, and sunflower seeds.",
    "Stir gently until the mixture is thickened slightly but still liquid enough for porridge-like consistency.",
    "Add a pinch of salt if desired.",
    "Serve immediately."
